 Twitter Web Application

  What is it?
  -----------

  The Twitter Web Application is written on top of Perl Dancer Web Application framework.
  Allows you to view the recent tweets of a specified screen name, people being followed
  by the specified screen name and the intersection of the people being followed between
  two screen names.

  Installation
  ------------

  Please see the file called INSTALL.  Platform specific notes can be
  found in README.platforms.

